des:
FIYE 101.9 Atlanta Radio (FIYE RADIO)is at the intersection of music and community progress, focused on promoting independent brands and businesses that embody our values of creativity, and authenticity. From local content creators to self-made entrepreneurs, we showcase a wide range of content, encouraging our audience to support independent creators and stay open to new ways to positively impact the world around them.

Most importantly, FIYE Radio is dedicated to influencing the culture in meaningful ways. Whether we're discussing social justice issues, highlighting grassroots movements, or celebrating cultural milestones, we're all about highlighting greatness. By involving our audience on air, online, and in the community, we start conversations, challenge the status quo, and inspire action. And with our fingers on the pulse of Atlanta’s vibrant scene, We are committed to making sure our listeners feel the heartbeat of Atlanta.
